1. Now supports to open a file directly from cloud drives by tapping on the file.

3. Added back In-app Upgrade in iZip free version. Now iZip users can upgrade through in-app purchase to the Premium version.
4. Added Spotlight search support for Files. Users now can search and open a file in iZip using Spotlight search.
5. Various bug fixed.
6. Build for iOS 12 and new iPhone devices.
